{"name": "python-ulid-django", "metadata": {"name": "python-ulid-django", "version": "1.2.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Framework :: Django", "Framework :: Django :: 4", "Framework :: Django :: 4.1", "Framework :: Django :: 4.2", "Framework :: Django :: 5.0", "Framework :: Django :: 5.1", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["django", "python-ulid"], "summary": "ULID (Universally Unique Lexicographically Sortable Identifier) support for Django.", "upload_time": 1733254412}, "documentation": ["# python-ulid-django\n\n[ULID (Universally Unique Lexicographically Sortable Identifier)][ulid-spec] support for\nDjango.\n\nThis package uses the ULID type implemented by [`python-ulid`][python-ulid].\n\n> This package is heavily inspired by [`django-ulid`][django-ulid]. The reason I'm\n> reinventing the wheel is that I want to use [`python-ulib`][python-ulid]'s\n> ULID implementation.\n\n## Usage\n\n### Installation\n\n```shell\npip install python-ulid-django\n```\n\n### Model Field\n\nYou can then add `ULIDField` to your Django model just like other fields.\n\nExample:\n\n```python\nfrom django.contrib.auth.models import AbstractUser\nfrom ulid import ULID\nfrom ulid_django.models import ULIDField\n\n\nclass User(AbstractUser):\n    id = ULIDField(primary_key=True, default=ULID, editable=False)\n```\n\n### URL Converter\n\nThere is also a URL converter can be used.\n\n```python\nfrom django.urls import path, register_converter\nfrom ulid import ULID\nfrom ulid_django.converters import ULIDConverter\n\n\ndef user_detail_view(request, user_id):\n    assert isinstance(user_id, ULID)\n    ...\n\n\nregister_converter(ULIDConverter, \"ulid\")\n\nurlpatterns = [\n    path(\"user/<ulid:user_id>/\", user_detail_view),\n    ...,\n]\n```\n\n## Development\n\nPrerequisite: [PDM](https://pdm-project.org/latest/)\n\nEnvironment setup: `pdm sync`\n\nRun linters: `pdm lint`\n\nTest: `pdm test`\n\n[ulid-spec]: https://github.com/ulid/spec\n\n[python-ulid]: https://github.com/mdomke/python-ulid\n\n[django-ulid]: https://github.com/ahawker/django-ulid\n"], "modules": [{"name": "ulid_django", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "ulid_django.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField", "bases": ["models.UUIDField"], "methods": [{"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField.to_python", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "ULID | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField.from_db_value", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "*_", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "**__", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "ULID | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField.get_prep_value", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "UUID | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField.get_db_prep_value", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "connection", "type": {"name": "BaseDatabaseWrapper", "xref": {"fqname": "django.db.backends.base.base.BaseDatabaseWrapper", "project": "django"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "prepared", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField.formfield", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "form_class", "type": {"name": "type[Field] | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "choices_form_class", "type": {"name": "type[ChoiceField] | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Field | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField._pyi_private_set_type", "type": {"name": "str | ULID", "xref": null, "params": null}, "documentation": ["type: ignore[assignment]"]}, {"name": "ulid_django.models.ULIDField._pyi_private_get_type", "type": {"name": "ULID", "xref": {"fqname": "ulid.ULID", "project": "python-ulid"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["type: ignore[assignment]"]}, {"name":